{
  "texts": [
    "To fine-tune the pre-trained BLIP model, we employed a dataset consisting of FFA images and their corresponding Chinese reports.",
    "During the training process, we randomly selected 1-9 images from each case as input for the model, ensuring a balanced representation of the arterial, venous, and late phases of FFA.",
    "All images were resized to 320×320 pixels.",
    "For the fine-tuning process, the model was trained with two NVIDIA Tesla V100 GPUs.",
    "The initial learning rate was set to 0.00002, with a weight decay of 0.05."
  ]
}